<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673>
    bibo:endPage "119" ;
    bibo:journal "Subterranean Biology" ;
    bibo:startPage "109" ;
    bibo:volume "34" ;
    dc:creator "Palacios-Vargas, Jose G." ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Acheroxenylla (Collembola, Hypogastruridae), first record from the Americas with description of a new species from a Peruvian cave" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figures1-4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figures5-7>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figures8-9>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figure10>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figures11-12> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figures1-4>
    dc:description "Figures 1 - 4. 1 Acheroxenylla lipsae sp. nov. 1, group of specimens floating on water close to the guano of oil birds 2 two specimens dorsal view just collected in ethanol 96 %; photos 1 and 2 by Josiane Lips 3 dorsal view 4 lateral view, photos 3 and 4 by Maira Montejo and Angela Arango, scale in photos 3 and 4 is 150 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414551" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figures5-7>
    dc:description "Figures 5 - 7. Acheroxenylla lipsae sp. nov. 5 ant IV dorsal view 6 head chaetotaxy 7 Tita I." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414552" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figures8-9>
    dc:description "Figures 8, 9. Acheroxenylla lipsae sp. nov. 8 dorsal chaetotaxy of Th. I - III 9 Tita III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414553" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Acheroxenylla lipsae sp. nov. Dorsal abdominal chaetotaxy." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414554" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.34.50673.figures11-12>
    dc:description "Figures 11, 12. Acheroxenylla lipsae sp. nov. 11. Ventral abdominal chaetotaxy from Abd. III to V, with retinaculum and furcula; 12. two mucrodens in lateral position." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414555" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

